---
title: Mexican Chicken & Garlic Quinoa Bowl with Creamy Slaw & Charred Corn Salsa
description: The secret to an amazing nourish bowl? Add fluffy garlic quinoa for heartiness, Mexican spiced chicken
breast for flavour, creamy aioli slaw, and a fresh salsa for garnish. Mix together for a truly magical result!
